  },
  {
    question: "What about evolving WhatsApp conversations?",
    answer: "Glazing conversations often evolve — a homeowner initially messages about one misted window, then notices three more, then asks whether it is worth upgrading to triple glazing while the units are being replaced. The AI maintains the thread and your lead summary consolidates every message, photo, and question into one complete brief."
