  },
  {
    question: "Can I take over a WhatsApp conversation?",
    answer: "Your own message in any thread transfers the conversation to you. The AI steps aside. Most glaziers let the AI handle the initial capture — glass type, frame material, quantity, postcode — then follow up personally to discuss specifications, arrange the measurement visit, and confirm the quotation."
  },
  {
